room_title: Escape room "Wonderland" by The Encrypted Escape in Green Bay
room_address: 1390 Bellevue St, Suite 105 Green Bay, WI 54311
room_description: Have you ever wondered what being lost within the crazy world of Alice’s Wonderland would be like? You will have one hour to twist your way through the rabbit hole, have tea with some mad hatters, and find your way out of the Queen’s evil fortress. Do you have what Alice had in order to escape Wonderland? Come and find out.
